      <title>拜登以电动汽车规则的时钟滴答作响来应对美中分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-04-15/biden-confronts-us-china-divide-with-clock-ticking-for-ev-rules</link>
